com.radaee.pdf

Class PDFV

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.radaee.pdf.PDFV

  • public class PDFV
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for PDFView, which is written by C/C++ codes
    this is a "timer-drive" view class, means that developers should call PDFV.draw in timer to show page-layouts.
    options for this class see: PDFVS class.
    Author:
    radaee

        Parameters:
        bitmap - Bitmap object allocated by APP.

      • Find

        public int Find(int dir)
        go find
        Parameters:
        dir - go backward if less than 0, otherwise go forward
        Returns:
        as following: 0: found in current page
